race.description: Make The Move To Midnite Handicap
race.comment: Narrow Wolverhampton (2400m) winner NAUGHTY NIALL (9) seems to know where the line is when fitted with cheekpieces. Ian Williams trains this previous course winner. May follow-up from a good draw in gate five. MR NUGGET (2) also scored narrowly at Wolverhampton (1900m) last time out and cannot be ruled out as a previous course and distance winner who might appreciate going back up in trip. KINGSCLERE (12) shaped as though this stiffer stamina test was worth exploring finishing fourth behind the main selection at Wolverhampton while she remains very much unexposed. Another to note is recent Redcar winner WOODLEIGH (4).
